11. How are government regulations impacting the OSB panels market?
Government regulations related to sustainable forestry and emissions control are impacting the OSB panels market.

12. What are the different types of OSB panels available in the market?
Types of OSB panels include OSB/1, OSB/2, OSB/3, and OSB/4, each with different performance characteristics.

13. What are the applications of OSB/1 panels?
OSB/1 panels are suitable for use in dry conditions and non-structural applications.

14. What are the applications of OSB/2 panels?
OSB/2 panels are suitable for use in dry conditions and general structural applications.

15. What are the applications of OSB/3 panels?
OSB/3 panels are suitable for use in humid conditions and load-bearing applications.

16. What are the applications of OSB/4 panels?
OSB/4 panels are suitable for use in humid conditions and heavy load-bearing applications.

