The COVID-19 pandemic has led to supply chain disruptions and a slowdown in construction activity, impacting the OSB panels market.

18. What are the market opportunities for OSB panels in the renewable energy sector?
The use of OSB panels in the construction of renewable energy infrastructure, such as wind turbine towers, presents a market opportunity for the OSB panels industry.

